descriptionHtml:
This is Asta clone from Eldergleam Sanctuary. I dont want to mess up with original files, so instead i added her clone and gave her some items and perks. She is good with a bow, sword, light armor, should be able to conjure flame atronach and heal herself, and she can avoid death once a day with so-called perk (Avoid Death)
Her voice is changed to Isolda's voice, because original FemaleNord doesnt have all lines needed
this is my first mod
